	std::cout << "The shining light of a new day dawns upon you. From a small village, you awaken and arise from your bed. The stories of legendary explorers discovering new lands and oceans have much influence over the youths of your village. You are no exception. You get dressed and prepare for a long journey. You hit the road with a small sack of food stuffs and your pittance of gold.\n";
