		std::cout << "The sun blazes on a sprawling city bustling with activity. The rich live in opulence at the city's center while the poor languish at the city's outer edge. The city's outer edge is a disgusting slum, with a dark, foul-smelling smog covering the area. Crime and disease run rampant. Garbage and sewage line the streets. From a pile of human feces and used toilet paper, you rise. Immediately, a gnome with a broken leg begins to hobble over to you. Screeching, 'GIVE ME YOUR GOLD, ALL YOUR GOLD!' (You lose 1000 gold) Cowering in fear, you throw the hobbling gnome all your gold. After losing all your gold, you leave this wretched city. You start your journey in a greatly depressed state.\n";
		gold -= 1000;
